Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下面要读哪本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前段时间大量的推理小说完好无损地漂流到了岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实有件事我一直想做做看  哪怕就一次也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实  就是像推理小说中的主人公那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想试着真正去和怪人决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去解决事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才想以此为蓝本来写小说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是清正先生的话应该能写好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请一定写一下试试
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会期待着的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我没有文采的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:25.42,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,去揭秘吧  侦探（后篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我之名为红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话那邀请帖果然是你发的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那绫音所看到的我  也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  百面怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想听到年轻少女的尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:02:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想看到她们恐怖的表情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先在那少女的皮肤上涂了岛上最痒的东部森林的山药汁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然会自然好转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过得要一周时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想立刻就治好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能使用这解毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快点把那个拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然…居然对我重要的客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把你作为敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进行排除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜小姐  稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要解毒药的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在满月还未消失之前抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么做的话  就全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  不能这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的声音是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是朔夜小姐把什么当作敌人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜小姐照顾周到特意为我们放的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一边洗澡一边看烟花也是很享受的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是红夜叉但也是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过好像被逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能躲开我的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是敌人但也值得钦佩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  先回月见亭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为事件会就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人好迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要泡到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得大家都住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一天马上就要过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:05:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的乐趣现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是马上要睡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃真是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上不单单只是睡觉的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  确实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一整晚努力的修行也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:21.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那凛到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,带行人大人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和他睡在同一被窝里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一整晚在里面卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是睡觉技能的特训吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小忍  我觉得不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  大姐头不能偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想…想和公子…一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃也想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说很大胆的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  行人和我同一个房间的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起睡的应该是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃不是每晚都睡一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  让我们一晚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在还没出嫁之前女孩子怎么就能做出这样的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家还是未成年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话真是没完没了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里轮到我出场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你浅薄的智慧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正起不到什么作用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么有什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  在行人洗澡回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请先回自己的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之后只剩下给行人的信而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,信…要写什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想与你一起共渡良宵  请来我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说  让行人自己来选
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是挑战书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  也许行人会谁都不选独自一人去空房间睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么让它们去空房间待命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等行人来了把他赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人最喜欢的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一切将在今晚揭晓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人…最喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么  当然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  也许是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛才不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照其行动规律来看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会假扮成某人然后混到大家里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,窥视等待引发下次事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么的话  请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是否是假货  我会识破他的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  真不愧是科学的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么特殊的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  只是想一个一个扯她们的脸来确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜小姐要是去扯的话  就算是真的皮肤也会扯掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜小姐伤害了客人  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么原始的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有更加科学性的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根据红外线透视
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根据声纹和体温的个体识别之类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能有那么便利的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是SF
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:31.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,(SF：Science  Fiction  超现实的作品)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为朔夜小姐的存在本身已经是SF了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在这里不能依靠科学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠直接的方法来把他逼到绝境了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直接的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  对侦探来说最大的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是顶头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.51,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,(顶头：相扑和摔跤的格斗手段之一，用自己的头部顶向对手进行攻击)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是用头脑  也就是推理力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等着吧  红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受这挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会来…不会来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是练习  练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下面才是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不能在公子面前太随意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也得稍微注重下仪表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  怎么还不来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了的话玩什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  已经看过信了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的人所在的地方  会是谁的房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是宫本武藏打倒佐佐木小次郎时的战法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁心智混乱之时忽然闪现一口气决出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会上当
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了尖叫  过来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍小姐  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,师…傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是因为激烈的按摩而动弹不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么按摩会那么激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来曾有什么人在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人类按摩椅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是谁会做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是红夜叉  千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了  真正的红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然那邀请帖是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在刚才绫音牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍就是第二个牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去  就会出现第三  第四个牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再让你擅自妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事情严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和行人单独两人渡过一夜的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会这样扑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,背后奇痒无比  难过死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手却够不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  再下面点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绫音皮肤真美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人…怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是因为太痒而进入了妄想世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也许会稍微轻松点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红夜叉那家伙接下来打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在新的牺牲者出现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点阻止的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是梅梅小姐的尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:12:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么沾在脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道又是山药汁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  身体有什么地方痒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…梅梅你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你选择我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…虽然还不值得夸耀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  忽然怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是平常害羞的梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:35.44,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,让行人大人看到害羞的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给那孩子所涂的不是山药汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给那孩子涂的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦沾到便会立即想做H的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蘑菇泥汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然解毒药在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但看来少年也不是不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅拜托你们俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.34,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫醒有点过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不使用这发笑的药了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这回不让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不错  就是这个状态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  刚才开始就那么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不是睡不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  尿床了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个敏捷的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里应该不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了  是凛的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么回来这里  命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为姐姐不带我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公子  你选择我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那像大叔一样的毫无疑问是真正的命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那样的话只能一个个找了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没理由就被打出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红夜叉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来梅梅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜这样打了她一下就让她睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才上面有可疑的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  在二楼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特大红豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  还醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红夜叉出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是看了信而过来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我放心了  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我最喜欢的人是小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等  行人你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人吧  怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那给你看证据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才所说的红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃的话  能分清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟每天都一起生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这个行人  和平常的感觉有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊  仔细看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我适可而止  离开小铃身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀…杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…这时候一般应该互相证明自己是真的才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:18.73,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这个是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁理你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点玩过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能让你逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经穷途末路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然在小说里不清楚你是谁就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我会在这里揭穿你的真实面目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然没有注意到被引诱上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有恐高症吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然怕的动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前邀请来的男人还能再稍微有点乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对做不到像那个男人那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不许…说绝对做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  解毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要…要落下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正如传言中那样是个很有趣的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得那孩子会如此中意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得涌出了创作欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…总有一天会在满月之时再会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能让他跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭那么点洞察力就像揭穿我的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还早得很
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他不服输的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见面时还是小心点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有时是会使用忍者招术的怪人红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有时以那事件为基础而写小说神秘的作家静丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过其真实身份是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这试炼如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正如千影所说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合第二代主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,令人期待的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然怪人的宿敌就该是拥有强烈的不服输精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那比什么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又能看到静丸的新作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上的读者都会非常高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过无论怎么说  已经约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会再次写新作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和静丸最重要的书迷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扮演红夜叉并开始写小说的契机是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了引起那位喜欢推理小说的书迷的注意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  我会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经早上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:21:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是不知道行人选择了谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉是有点遗憾却又松了一口气的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  我们噩梦般的一晚结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  红夜叉的牺牲者太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红夜叉  这愤怒总有一天会偿还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天  要揭穿你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:12.14,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,月见亭的杀人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉自己作为小说的原型  心情好复杂
